### Testing the emoji reaction feature:
In any of your chats, hover over a message, click on the emoji icon.
![][image1]

[image1]: <data:image/png;base64,>
After that, you can see emojis to choose from,

![][image15]

[image15]: <data:image/png;base64,>
 and you can observe the reaction displayed.

![][image16]

[image16]: <data:image/png;base64,>

### Testing the notes on posts feature:
Click **3 dots** to open the actions list on the post, and you will see a **manage-notes** button.
![][image2]

[image2]: <data:image/png;base64,>
Click on **manage-notes** and make your notes using the form that pops up.

![][image3]

[image3]: <data:image/png;base64,>
### Share post to chat:
Under a post, you can see a button for **sharing a post**. After you click, you will see a pop up with your chats. Press **send** next to the chat label that you want the post to be sent to.

![][image10]

[image10]: <data:image/png;base64,>

![][image11]

[image11]: <data:image/png;base64,>


Please note that there are accompanying screenshots embedded within this document. In order to see them, please open this file in your editor.
